a%20restaurant%20in%20the%20city%20%E2%80%93%20and%20took%20action%20against%20the%20organisers%20of%20the%20event%20instead%20of%20those%20who%20had%20disrupted%20it.%20Four%20people%20%E2%80%93%20including%20those%20who%20own%20Marley%E2%80%99s%20Joint%20Bistro%20where%20the%20event%20was%20held%20and%20members%20of%20the%20organising%20body%2C%20Hyderabad%20Cinephiles%20%E2%80%93%20were%20arrested.%20They%20have%20been%20charged%20under%20Sections%20143%20(unlawful%20assembly)%2C%20290%20(public%20nuisance)%2C%20295A%20(outraging%20religious%20feelings)%20and%20149%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatwardhan%E2%80%99s%20documentary%20traces%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20movement%20of%20the%201990s%20and%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20on%20December%206%2C%201992.%20In%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fram-ke-naam-movie-anand-patwardhan-on-janmabhoomi-politics%5C%22%3Erecent%20interview%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Patwardhan%20said%20he%20was%20disappointed%20that%20the%20movie%20is%20still%20so%20relevant%2C%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20being%20inaugurated%20on%20January%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20Hyderabad%20Cinephiles%20have%20detailed%20what%20happened%20and%20criticised%20both%20the%20police%20and%20the%20state%20Congress%20government.%20Read%20the%20full%20statement%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%2020%20January%2C%20screening%20and%20discussion%20of%20Anand%20Patwardhan%E2%80%99s%20documentary%20%E2%80%98Ram%20ke%20Naam%E2%80%99%20was%20organised%20by%20Hyderabad%20Cinephiles%20at%20Marley%E2%80%99s%20Joint%20Bistro%2C%20Sainikpuri.%20The%20screening%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20even%20reached%20the%20midpoint%20when%20around%2010%20people%20entered%20and%20disrupted%20the%20program.%20They%20were%20pointing%20their%20fingers%20at%20the%20organisers%20and%20participants%20yelling%2C%20stating%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20illegal%20to%20screen%20this%20movie%20and%20that%20their%20religious%20sentiments%20were%20hurt.%20They%20tried%20to%20pull%20and%20tear%20the%20screen.%20They%20abused%20the%20organisers%20and%20used%20misogynist%20slurs%20and%20termed%20the%20organisers%20as%20anti-Hindu.%20They%20created%20such%20a%20ruckus%20that%20the%20screening%20had%20to%20be%20stopped%20midway.%20Few%20moments%20later%2C%20the%20police%20also%20appeared%20at%20the%20scene.%20The%20organisers%20tried%20to%20explain%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20a%20banned%20movie%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20available%20on%20YouTube%2C%20but%20they%20were%20not%20ready%20to%20listen%20to%20them.%20The%20film%20got%20a%20U%20censor%20certificate%20in%201992%20(for%20unrestricted%20public%20exhibition).%20It%20won%20a%20National%20Award%20and%20a%20Filmfare%20award%20that%20year.%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20ruled%20that%20it%20should%20be%20telecasted%20on%20primetime%20Doordarshan.%20But%20despite%20all%20the%20facts%20provided%20by%20the%20organisers%2C%20the%20police%20took%20the%20organiser%2C%20participants%20and%20the%20cafe%20owner%20to%20the%20Neredmet%20police%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20goons%20who%20disrupted%20the%20program%20were%20present%20at%20the%20police%20station%2C%20but%20instead%20of%20taking%20any%20action%20against%20them%2C%20the%20police%20started%20questioning%20the%20organisers%20and%20participants%20themselves.%20An%20organiser%20and%20a%20participant%20were%20kept%20in%20police%20lock%20up%20throughout%20the%20night.%20The%20police%20did%20not%20allow%20their%20lawyer%20to%20meet%20them.%20On%2021%20January%2C%20the%20police%20filed%20cases%20against%20the%20organiser%2C%20a%20participant%20and%20the%20two%20cafe%20owners%20under%20sections%20143%2C%20290%2C%20295%20(A)%20R%2FW%20149%20of%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%20The%20police%20also%20confiscated%20a%20projector%2C%20loudspeaker%20used%20in%20the%20screening.%20The%20mobile%20phones%20of%20one%20of%20the%20organiser%20and%20a%20participant%20were%20also%20seized.%20All%20the%20accused%20were%20released%20yesterday%20after%20being%20presented%20before%20the%20magistrate%2C%20but%20the%20formal%20bail%20order%20has%20not%20been%20received%20by%20them%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20incident%20is%20yet%20another%20instance%20of%20increasing%20curb%20on%20the%20freedom%20of%20expression%20in%20the%20country%20and%20attacks%20against%20the%20democratic%20right%20of%20citizens.%20Telangana%20is%20a%20state%20ruled%20by%20the%20Congress%20party%20and%20this%20incident%20is%20quite%20telling%20of%20their%20claims%20of%20secularism%20and%20democracy%20as%20the%20Hyderabad%20police%2C%20instead%20of%20acting%20against%20the%20unlawful%20disruption%20by%20the%20right%20wing%20people%20and%20ensuring%20that%20the%20screening%20goes%20on%2C%20clearly%20acted%20in%20a%20unconstitutional%20manner%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20right%20wing%20goons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leaders%20of%20Congress%20have%20openly%20called%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Sangh%20Parivar%20fascist%20but%20this%20action%20contradicts%20those%20statements.%20They%20have%20emphasised%20on%20the%20need%20for%20secularism%20but%20this%20was%20the%20time%20to%20ensure%20it%2C%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20democratic%20secular%20rights%20of%20people%20are%20preserved%2C%20but%20that%20did%20not%20happen.%20We%20are%20afraid%20that%20it%20does%20not%20matter%20which%20party%20is%20in%20government%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20police%20action.%20The%20fascisisation%20of%20police%20and%20the%20internal%20capture%20of%20state%20power%20by%20the%20RSS%20is%20clearly%20the%20reality%20of%20our%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705901769000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22110551%2Fdownload-20.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhyderabad-hindutva-groups-disrupt-screening-of-ram-ke-naam-organisers-arrested%22%2C%22summary%22%3A