n%20Sunday%20and%20was%20expected%20to%20land%20in%20Prague%20just%20after%2010%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20half%20an%20hour%20into%20the%20flight%2C%C2%A0it%20turned%20around%20over%20the%20Strait%20of%20Dover%20and%20came%20back%20to%20the%20UK%2C%20according%20to%20flight%20path%20data%20from%20FlightRadar24.%20The%20plane%20flew%20back%20to%20Heathrow%20and%20touched%20down%20at%208.41%20am.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20soon%20as%20the%20plane%20landed%2C%C2%A0several%20fire%20engines%20rushed%20towards%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20British%20Airways%20spokesperson%20blamed%20a%20'technical%20issue'%20for%20the%20quick%20about-turn%2C%20though%20they%20did%20not%20specify%20what%20had%20caused%20the%20pilots%20to%20choose%20to%20return%20to%20Heathrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBritish%20Airways%20said%20in%20a%20statement%3A%20''We're%20sorry%20for%20the%20delay%20in%20our%20customers'%20journey%20after%20the%20aircraft%20returned%20to%20Heathrow%20as%20a%20precaution.%20Our%20teams%20looked%20after%20them%20whilst%20they%20waited%20to%20board%20a%20replacement%20aircraft%20to%20continue%20their%20journey.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20comes%20as%20the%20airline%20cancelled%20more%20than%20three%20dozen%20flights%20from%20Heathrow%20on%20Sunday%2C%20because%20of%20Storm%20Isha.%20Yesterday%2C%C2%A0A%20British%20Airways%20flight%20was%20unable%20to%20land%20due%20to%20the%20strong%20winds%20at%20Heathrow.%C2%A0The%20pilot%20was%20forced%20to%20take%20off%20again%20and%20recircle%20several%20times%20before%20it%20could%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EData%20from%20FlightRadar24%20revealed%20that%20several%20flights%20were%20forced%20to%20change%20their%20paths%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBritish%20Airways%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CLike%20other%20airlines%2C%20we%20have%20had%20to%20make%20schedule%20adjustments%20due%20to%20the%20adverse%20weather%20conditions%20across%20the%20UK%20and%20Europe%20caused%20by%20Storm%20Isha.%20We've%20apologised%20to%20our%20customers%20for%20the%20disruption%20to%20their%20travel%20plans%20and%20our%20teams%20are%20working%20hard%20to%20get%20them%20on%20their%20way%20as%20quickly%20as%20possible.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20back%2C%20a%20JetBlue%20Airbus%20A321%20bound%20for%20California%20aborted%20takeoff%20on%20the%20John%20F.%20Kennedy%20Airport%20runway%20after%20reports%20of%20a%20fire%20aboard%2C%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F01%2F14%2Fmetro%2Fnyc-jetblue-flight-aborts-takeoff-at-jfk-over-mechanical-problem-scare%2F%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0reported.%20As%20per%20the%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%20(FAA)%2C%20the%20aircraft%20was%20in%20the%20process%20of%20departing%20at%20approximately%208%3A30%20p.m.%20when%20the%20crew%20alerted%20the%20control%20tower%20to%20the%20issue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705896360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-02%2F9j08bhno_british-airways-boeing-747_625x300_10_February_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbritish-airways-flight-makes-emergency-landing-at-heathrow-after-fumes-in-the-cockpit-4908350%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20British%20Airways%20spokesperson%20blamed%20a%20'technical%20issue'%20for%20the%20quick%20about-turn%2C%20though%20they%20did%20not%20specify%20what%20had%20caused%20the%20pilots%20to%20choose%20to%20return%20to%20Heathrow.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbritish-airways-flight-makes-emergency-landing-at-heathrow-after-fumes-in-the-cockpit-4908350%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbritish-airways-flight-makes-emergency-landing-at-heathrow-after-fumes-in-the-cockpit-4908350%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news