3E%3Cstrong%3EIndian%20defence%20presence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20key%20element%20of%20new%20president%20Muizzu%E2%80%99s%20successful%20presidential%20campaign%20was%20the%20demand%20for%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20Indian%20military%20forces.%20Muizzu%20had%20said%20that%20their%20presence%20was%20a%20violation%20of%20Maldivian%20sovereignty.%20Upon%20assuming%20office%2C%20Muizzu%20formally%20requested%20the%20removal%20of%20Indian%20defence%20personnel.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20had%20last%20October%20highlighted%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22about%3Ablank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E523%20Maldivian%20lives%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20been%20saved%20in%20500%20medical%20evacuations%20for%20last%20five%20years%20by%20Indian%20personnel%20manning%20the%20aircrafts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Maldives%20president%20had%20last%20month%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpresidency.gov.mv%2FPress%2FArticle%2F29481%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eannounced%20the%20start%20of%20a%20new%20air%20ambulance%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20service%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Maldivian%20airlines%20from%20March%202024.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20as%20both%20countries%20are%20currently%20in%20talks%2C%20Maldives%20has%20given%20a%20deadline%20of%20March%2015%20to%20India%20for%20removing%20any%20Indian%20military%20officers%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20death%20of%20the%20boy%20has%2C%20therefore%2C%20led%20opposition%20members%20to%20claim%20that%20he%20could%20have%20been%20saved%20if%20the%20Indian%20planes%20had%20been%20put%20to%20service.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOpposition%20members%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20Maldivian%20government%20has%20stopped%20the%20operation%20of%20the%20three%20Indian%20aircraft%2C%20but%20there%20is%20no%20official%20confirmation%20from%20New%20Delhi%20or%20Mal%C3%A9.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Maldives%20president%20asserted%20last%20month%20that%20the%20government%20had%20not%20issued%20an%20order%20to%20halt%20the%20operation%20of%20the%20planes.%20However%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20mention%20of%20any%20Dornier%20or%20helicopter%20operations%20in%20the%20Maldivian%20media%20since%20the%20new%20government%20took%20over.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EState%20of%20affairs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Maldivian%20National%20Defence%20Force%20(MNDF)%20used%20to%20routinely%20report%20with%20photographs%20of%20medical%20evacuation%20done%20through%20the%20Dornier%20or%20helicopters.%20The%20last%20such%20press%20release%20related%20to%20a%20medical%20evacuation%20through%20a%20Dornier%20was%20issued%20by%20MNDF%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmndf.gov.mv%2Fmndf%2Fen%2Fnews-article-dhiv.php%3Farticle%3D4700%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EOctober%2010.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20December%2C%20a%20Maldivian%20media%20outlet%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAdhadhu%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fenglish.adhadhu.com%2Farticle%2F47371%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eraised%20questions%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20about%20why%20the%20MNDF%20did%20not%20deploy%20the%20Dornier%20aircraft%20for%20search%20and%20rescue%20operations%20when%20a%20man%20went%20missing%20while%20searching%20for%20lobsters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDue%20to%20the%20rising%20criticism%20about%20not%20putting%20in%20service%20the%20Indian%20plane%2C%20the%20Maldivian%20defence%20minister%20Ghassan%20Gayoom%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmgmaumoon%2Fstatus%2F1748693255997264126%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eclaimed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20more%20than%2093%25%20of%20medical%20evacuation%20since%202021%20was%20done%20by%20Maldivian%20airlines.%20He%20also%20claimed%20that%20standard%20operating%20procedures%20did%20not%20require%20any%20permission%20from%20the%20President%20for%20operating%20emergency%20evacuation%20flights.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPresident%20Muizzu%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpresidency.gov.mv%2FPress%2FArticle%2F29670%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eexpressed%20condolences%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20about%20the%20death%20of%20the%20boy%20and%20ordered%20the%20reform%20of%20protocols%20for%20emergency%20transfers%20of%20patients.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20state-run%20health%20insurance%20company%2C%20Aasandha%20Company%20Ltd%20claimed%20that%20the%20planned%20evacuation%20flight%20had%20been%20delayed%20due%20to%20last-minute%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpsmnews.mv%2Fen%2F131931%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etechnical%20issue%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D.%20The%20national%20carrier%20Maldivian%20declared%20on%20Sunday%20that%20it%20will%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fenglish.adhadhu.com%2Farticle%2F48658%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eprioritize%20medical%20evacuations%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20over%20scheduled%20flights.%20The%20health%20ministry%20announced%20that%20it%20will%20review%20whether%20there%20was%20any%20negligence%20in%20the%20procedures%20followed%20before%20the%20evacuation%20of%20the%20boy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20government%20in%20a%20defensive%20mode%2C%20the%20opposition%20dominated-Parliament%20announced%20their%20own%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.sun.mv%2F87162%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Einquiry%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20into%20the%20death%20of%20the%20boy%20through%20the%20parliamentary%20committee%20on%20human%20rights%20and%20gender%20which%20held%20a%20meeting%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22about%3Ablank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESun%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20opposition%20MP%20Rozaina%20said%20at%20the%20parliamentary%20committee%20meeting%20that%20strained%20ties%20with%20India%20was%20impacting%20Maldivian%20citizens%20and%20criticised%20the%20stoppage%20of%20use%20of%20the%20three%20aircraft%20donated%20by%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20MDP%20member%20of%20parliament%20Meekail%20Naseem%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmickailnaseem%2Fstatus%2F1748655097993646272%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etweeted%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20pay%20with%20their%20lives%20to%20satisfy%20the%20President%E2%80%99s%20animosity%20towards%20India%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Not%20doing%20enough%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20opposition%20is%20trying%20to%20corner%20the%20government%2C%20Muizzu%20is%20also%20under%20pressure%20from%20his%20estranged%20former%20colleague%2C%20former%20President%20Abdulla%20Yameen%20for%20not%20doing%20enough%20to%20remove%20Indian%20military%20from%20Maldives.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuizzu%20had%20got%20the%20opposition%20ticket%20for%20the%20Presidential%20elections%2C%20as%20Yameen%20could%20not%20contest%20due%20to%20his%20conviction.%20Yameen%20had%20reluctantly%20supported%20him%2C%20but%20after%20the%20presidential%20elections%2C%20both%20of%20them%20fell%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20former%20President%2C%20who%20is%20the%20original%20architect%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98India%20Out%E2%80%99%20campaign%20to%20demand%20the%20removal%20of%20Indian%20military%2C%20left%20the%20coalition%20and%20formed%20his%20own%20party.%20While%20he%20was%20removed%20from%20jail%2C%20Yameen%20has%20not%20been%20released%20as%20demanded%20by%20his%20supporters%20and%20remains%20in%20house%20arrest.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20a%20party%20meeting%20over%20the%20weekend%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.mv%2Fnews%2F31149%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20former%20President%20criticised%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20government%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Efor%20slowing%20down%20its%20initial%20attempts%20to%20force%20India%20to%20withdraw%20its%20personnel.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReferring%20to%20a%20minister%20claiming%20that%20the%20expulsion%20of%20Indian%20military%20would%20not%20be%20easy%2C%20Yameen%20said%20that%20he%20was%20disappointed.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20very%20disheartening%20to%20hear%20these%20words%20from%20a%20Minister%20of%20the%20President%E2%80%99s%20Office%20of%20a%20government%20that%20came%20with%20immense%20courage%20and%20resolve%20to%20remove%20the%20Indian%20troops%20from%20Maldives.%20Nothing%20will%20be%20easy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENext%20month%2C%20Maldives%20is%20set%20to%20conduct%20parliamentary%20elections%2C%20serving%20as%20a%20gauge%20of%20the%20Muizzu%20government%E2%80%99s%20popularity%20following%20Yameen%E2%80%99s%20exit%20and%20its%20actions%20that%20may%20have%20strained%20relations%20with%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705895204000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F14103358%2FGDvFFVLbgAAmZK2.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fmaldives-muizzu-indian-military-boy-death%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20is%20heightened%20political%20sensitivity%20over%20the%20death%20as%20it%20comes%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20Maldives%20government%20demanding%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20Indian%20military%20which%20is%20stationed%20in%20the%20archipelago%20nation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fmaldives-muizzu-indian-military-boy-death%22%2C%22cdnAmp