%20the%20Iraqi%20politician's%20office%20said%2C%20a%20day%20after%20pro-Iran%20militants%20struck%20US%20forces%20in%20the%20country.%20The%20meeting%20in%20Baghdad%20with%20Ambassador%20Alina%20Romanowski%20comes%20amid%20soaring%20regional%20tensions.%20Maliki%2C%20an%20influential%20figure%20in%20Iraqi%20politics%20and%20one%20of%20the%20top%20leaders%20of%20a%20pro-Iranian%20bloc%2C%20discussed%20with%20Romanowski%20%26quot%3Bthe%20future%20of%20bilateral%20relations%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20US%20and%20%26quot%3Bthe%20escalation%20in%20regional%20tensions%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20statement%20from%20his%20office%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Firaq-ex-pm-meets-us-envoy-after-strike%2Farticleshow%2F107040457.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Firaq-ex-pm-meets-us-envoy-after-strike%2Famp_articleshow%2F107040457.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Firaq-ex-pm-meets-us-envoy-after-strike%2Famp_articleshow%2F107040457.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Drones%2C%20Snipers%20And%20Bomb%20Squads%20Across%20Ayodhya%20Ahead%20Of%20Ram%20Temple%20Event%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20temple%20town%20of%20Ayodhya%20is%20all%20set%20to%20welcome%20Lord%20Ram%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20scheduled%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20at%20the%20newly%20constructed%20Ram%20Mandir%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'Pran%20Pratishtha'%20of%20the%20idol%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%20--%20the%20childhood%20form%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20--%20will%20be%20attended%20by%20people%20from%20all%20walks%20of%20life%2C%20including%20representatives%20of%20major%20spiritual%20and%20religious%20sects%20of%20the%20country%2C%20representatives%20of%20various%20tribal%20communities%20and%20prominent%20personalities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ceremony%20will%20begin%20at%2012%3A20%20pm%2C%20and%20according%20to%20the%20temple's%20trust%2C%20it%20is%20expected%20to%20end%20by%201%20pm.%20Following%20this%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20will%20address%20the%20gathering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20prime%20minister%20will%20also%20interact%20with%20'shramjeevis'%20associated%20with%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20temple%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Shri%20Ram%20Janmbhoomi%20Teerth%20Kshetra%20Trust%2C%20which%20is%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20construction%20and%20management%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%20will%20also%20visit%20Kuber%20Tila%2C%20where%20an%20ancient%20Shiv%20temple%20has%20been%20restored.%20He%20will%20perform%20a%20'pooja'%20there%2C%20the%20member%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20magnificent%20Ram%20Janmbhoomi%20Mandir%20or%20Ram%20temple%20has%20been%20constructed%20in%20the%20traditional%20Nagara%20style.%20Its%20length%20(east-west)%20is%20380%20feet%3B%20width%20250%20feet%20and%20height%20161%20feet.%20It%20is%20supported%20by%20a%20total%20of%20392%20pillars%20and%20has%2044%20doors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pillars%20and%20walls%20of%20the%20temple%20showcase%20intricately%20sculpted%20depictions%20of%20Hindu%20deities%2C%20gods%20and%20goddesses.%20In%20the%20main%20sanctum%20sanctorum%20at%20the%20temple's%20ground%20floor%2C%20the%20idol%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%20has%20been%20placed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20consecration%20rituals%20for%20the%20'Pran%20Pratishtha'%20started%20from%20the%20Saryu%20river%20on%20January%2016%20and%20will%20be%20completed%20on%20Monday%20afternoon%20in%20the%20'abhijeet%20muhurta'%2C%20according%20to%20the%20trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELakhs%20of%20people%20are%20expected%20to%20watch%20the%20event%20live%20on%20TV%20and%20online%20platforms%20as%20the%20central%20government%20has%20announced%20a%20half-day%20off%20on%20January%2022%20and%20many%20states%20followed%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETemples%20across%20the%20country%20have%20announced%20special%20festivities%20on%20the%20occasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20Washington%20DC%20to%20Paris%20to%20Sydney%2C%20events%20have%20been%20also%20planned%20in%20various%20parts%20of%20the%20world%20by%20either%20the%20Vishva%20Hindu%20Parishad%20(VHP)%20or%20Hindu%20diaspora%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFourteen%20couples%20from%20various%20parts%20of%20India%20will%20be%20the%20'yajmaans'%20(hosts)%20for%20the%20'Pran%20Pratishtha'%20of%20the%20new%2051-inch%20idol%20of%20Ram%20Lalla.%20The%20idol%20was%20sculpted%20by%20Mysuru-based%20Arun%20Yogiraj%20and%20was%20placed%20in%20the%20sanctum%20sanctorum%20of%20the%20temple%20last%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ram%20temple%20has%20been%20decorated%20with%20%26quot%3Brich%20stocks%26quot%3B%20of%20flowers%20and%20special%20lights%20and%20the%20entire%20city%20is%20drenched%20in%20religious%20fervour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStreetlights%20on%20flyovers%20have%20been%20decorated%20with%20artwork%20depicting%20Lord%20Ram%20as%20well%20as%20cutouts%20of%20bow%20and%20arrow%2C%20and%20ornamental%20lampposts%20carry%20designs%20themed%20on%20the%20traditional%20%26quot%3BRamanandi%20tilak%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20multi-layer%20security%20cover%20is%20in%20place%20in%20Ayodhya%20for%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%2C%20with%2010%2C000%20CCTV%20cameras%20and%20drones%20equipped%20with%20artificial%20intelligence%20keeping%20an%20eye%20on%20the%20movement%20of%20people%20and%20police%20personnel%20in%20plain%20clothes%20deployed%20at%20the%20venue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMovable%20barriers%20with%20barbed%20wires%20attached%20to%20them%20can%20be%20spotted%20at%20every%20prominent%20crossroad%20in%20the%20temple%20city%2C%20as%20police%20use%20them%20to%20regulate%20traffic%2C%20especially%20during%20VVIP%20movements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMultiple%20NDRF%20teams%20trained%20to%20tackle%20chemical%2C%20biological%2C%20radiological%20and%20nuclear%20attacks%2C%20drowning%20incidents%20and%20disasters%20like%20earthquakes%20have%20been%20deployed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESnipers%C2%A0are%20also%20deployed%20on%20rooftops%20and%20important%20locations.%20Besides%2C%20Intelligence%20Bureau%20and%20RAW%20are%20also%20keeping%20an%20eye%20on%20the%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20more%20than%207%2C000%20people%20are%20on%20the%20list%20of%20invitees%20for%20the%20event%2C%20the%20select%20list%20features%20506%20A-listers.%20Bollywood%20superstar%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%2C%20business%20tycoons%20Mukesh%20Ambani%20and%20Gautam%20Adani%2C%20and%20sporting%20icon%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%20are%20among%20the%20prominent%20people%20invited%20to%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20attending%20the%20%26quot%3BPran%20Prathishtha%26quot%3B%20also%20include%20people%20linked%20to%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20agitation.%20Almost%20all%20opposition%20leaders%20invited%20to%20the%20ceremony%20have%20declined%20to%20be%20in%20attendance%2C%20with%20the%20Congress%20calling%20it%20a%20%26quot%3BBJP-RSS%20event%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20consecration%20ceremony%20is%20being%20held%20after%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20the%20temple's%20construction%2C%20made%20possible%20by%20a%20historic%20Supreme%20Court%20judgment%20in%202019%20on%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi-Babri%20Masjid%20title%20suit.%20The%20Hindu%20litigants%20argued%20that%20the%20Babri%20Mosque%20was%20constructed%20at%20the%20site%20of%20a%20temple%20marking%20the%20birthplace%20of%20Lord%20Ram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201992%2C%20the%2016th%20century%20mosque%20was%20demolished%20by%20%26quot%3Bkar%20sevaks%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705892580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fkht7tn3o_ayodhya-security_625x300_22_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdrones-snipers-and-bomb-squads-across-ayodhya-ahead-of-ram-temple-event-4907831%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%