how%2F107038698.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20At%20Ram%20Temple%20Inauguration%20Today%2C%20History%20At%20Ayodhya%3A%2010%20Points%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20consecration%20ceremony%20will%20be%20celebrated%20across%20the%20country%20and%20Indians%20abroad%20with%20special%20prayers%20and%20various%20programmes%20at%20local%20temples.%20The%20occasion%20has%20been%20hailed%20as%20a%20Diwali%20--%20the%20festivities%20that%20marked%20Lord%20Ram's%20homecoming%20after%20the%20battle%20with%20Ravan%20and%20temples%20and%20houses%20have%20been%20strung%20with%20festive%20lighting.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPM%20Modi%20has%20been%20observing%20a%20series%20of%20strict%2011-day%20religious%20rituals%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20at%20noon.%20He%20will%20also%20address%20the%20gathering%20on%20the%20occasion%2C%20read%20a%20statement%20from%20his%20office.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThe%20historic%20Pran%20Pratishtha%20ceremony%20will%20be%20attended%20by%20representatives%20of%20all%20major%20spiritual%20and%20religious%20sects%20of%20the%20country.%20People%20from%20all%20walks%20of%20life%20including%20representatives%20of%20various%20tribal%20communities%20will%20also%20attend%20the%20ceremony%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPM%20Modi%20will%20interact%20with%20labourers%20who%20have%20been%20building%20the%20Ram%20temple.%20He%20would%20also%20visit%20Kuber%20Tila%2C%20where%20the%20ancient%20temple%20of%20Lord%20Shiv%20has%20been%20restored%2C%20and%20offer%20prayers.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20380x250%20feet%20temple%20is%20being%20built%20in%20the%20traditional%20north-Indian%20Nagara%20style.%20Its%20392%20pillars%2C%2044%20doors%20and%20walls%20have%20elaborate%20carvings%20of%20gods%20and%20goddesses.%20The%20idol%20of%20five-year-old%20Lord%20Ram%20has%20been%20placed%20at%20the%20sanctum%20sanctorum.%20The%20Kuber%20Tila%20stands%20at%20the%20southwestern%20part%20of%20the%20complex.%20Near%20the%20temple%20is%20a%20well%20(Sita%20koop)%2C%20believed%20to%20be%20dating%20back%20to%20the%20ancient%20era.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EVarious%20leaders%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20ideological%20mentor%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20have%20already%20been%20camping%20out%20at%20Ayodhya%2C%20which%20has%20prepared%20to%20receive%20over%2011%2C000%20visitors.%20Over%20the%20last%20weeks%2C%20the%20sleepy%20temple%20town%20has%20had%20an%20international%20airport%20and%20a%20renovated%20railway%20station.%20Hotels%2C%20guest%20houses%20and%20homestays%20have%20mushroomed%2C%20bursting%20it%20at%20the%20seams%20and%20bringing%20in%20the%20long%20awaited%20economic%20boom.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20opening%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20--%20which%20has%20been%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20a%20decades-long%20political%20storm%20--%20has%20been%20cold-shouldered%20by%20most%20Opposition%20parties%20including%20the%20Congress%2C%20Left%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%20and%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20which%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20gaining%20political%20mileage%20from%20religion%20on%20an%20election%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20hit%20back%2C%20censuring%20all%20who%20declined%20the%20invite%2C%20including%20the%20Congress's%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury.%20Calling%20the%20parties%20anti-Hindu%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20declared%20that%20they%20will%20get%20their%20punishment%20from%20the%20people%20at%20the%20hustings.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20event%20has%20also%20drawn%20other%20controversies%20--%20including%20the%20one%20that%20involves%20the%20Shankaracharyes%20of%20four%20premier%20monasteries%20staying%20away.%20The%20Puri%20and%20Joshimath%20Shankaracharyas%20have%20said%20consecration%20of%20an%20incomplete%20temple%20cannot%20be%20held.%20They%20have%20also%20questioned%20why%20PM%20Modi%20will%20be%20inside%20the%20sanctum%20sanctorum%20when%20the%20Shankaracharyas%20have%20been%20allotted%20seats%20outside.%20The%20event%2C%20they%20have%20alleged%2C%20is%20being%20given%20a%20political%20angle.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20building%20of%20the%20temple%20started%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20in%20a%20landmark%20judgment%20of%202019%2C%20awarded%20the%20disputed%20land%20for%20a%20temple%20and%20asked%20that%20Muslims%20be%20given%20an%20alternate%20plot%20for%20a%20mosque.%20The%20matter%2C%20which%20went%20to%20court%20shortly%20after%20Independence%2C%20had%20escalated%20after%20hundreds%20of%20Karsevaks%20razed%20a%2016th%20Century%20mosque%20on%20the%20site%2C%20believing%20it%20was%20built%20over%20a%20temple%20marking%20the%20birthplace%20of%20Lord%20Ram.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705887060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Ff9qvokrg_ayodhya_625x300_22_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fayodhya-ram-temple-ram-temple-ram-temple-opening-pm-to-attend-mega-ram-temple-inauguration-in-ayodhya-today-10-points-4907766%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20a%2050-year-project%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20long%20awaited%20by%20many%2C%20will%20take%20place%20today.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20will%20fly%20to%20Ayodhya%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20ceremony%2C%20which%20will%20be%20telecast%20live.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fayodhya-ram-temple-ram-temple-ram-temple-opening-pm-to-attend-mega-ram-temple-inauguration-in-ayodhya-today-10-points-4907766%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fayodhya-ram-temple-ram-temple-ram-temple-opening-pm-to-attend-mega-ram-temple-inauguration-in-ayodhya-today-10-points-4907766%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fayodhya-ram-temple-ram-temple-ram-temple-opening-pm-to-attend-mega-ram-temple-inauguration-in-ayodhya-today-10-points-4907766%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Power%20Is%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Ram%2C%20His%20Faith%2C%20His%20Trade'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21150907%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-21-at-1.25.10-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVaranasi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Mughal%20prince%20Dara%20Shikoh%20granted%20the%20patta%2C%20or%20deed%2C%20for%20the%20supervision%20of%20the%20Vishwanath%20temple%2C%20in%20Varanasi%2C%20to%20the%20forefathers%20of%20mahant%20Rajendra%20Prasad%20Tiwari%20in%20the%2017th%20century.%20Since%20then%2C%20over%2010%20generations%2C%20his%20family%20oversaw%20the%20ritual%20tradition%20of%20the%20temple%20until%2C%20in%201983%2C%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20deprived%20them%20of%20administrative%20powers.%20The%20rituals%20followed%20there%20are%20largely%20still%20those%20the%20Tiwaris%20determined%2C%20although%20alterations%20have%20been%20made%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETiwari%20was%20a%20strident%20critic%20of%20the%20Vishwanath%20Temple%20Corridor%2C%20a%20pet%20project%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%2C%20which%20was%20developed%20after%20demolishing%20several%20ancient%20temples%20housing%20an%20estimated%20286%20shivlings.%20These%20were%20uprooted%20and%20thrown%20away%3B%20many%20broke%3B%20only%20146%20could%20be%20recovered%20and%20are%20stored%20at%20the%20police%20station%20of%20Lanka%2C%20a%20locality%20in%20Varanasi%2C%20where%20their%20worship%20is%20still%20carried%20out%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20demolition%20deeply%20upset%20Tiwari%2C%20who%20often%20expressed%20his%20angst%20and%20anger%20at%20the%20mindless%20remaking%20of%20Varanasi%E2%80%99s%20sacred%20spaces.%20But%20that%20was%20in%20the%20past%2C%20I%20thought%2C%20believing%20Tiwari%20would%20have%20forgiven%20Modi%20amidst%20the%20extraordinary%20and%20orchestrated%20buzz%20over%20the%20idol%20consecration%20at%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20projected%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20%E2%80%9CHindu%20civilisational%20resurrection%E2%80%9D.%20Would%20he%2C%20like%20many%2C%20be%20celebrating%20January%2022%20in%20a%20special%20way%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20no%20attachment%20to%20today%E2%80%99s%20event%2C%20which%20is%20not%20a%20religious%20one.%20It%20is%20an%20event%20for%20implementing%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%20agenda%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tiwari%20says.%20He%20promptly%20asks%3A%20Would%20I%20expect%20him%20to%20participate%20in%20a%20religious%20event%20sponsored%20by%2C%20say%2C%20a%20film%20star%3F%20Today%E2%80%99s%20event%20is%20no%20different%2C%20for%20it%20has%20been%20organised%20to%20feed%20the%20vanity%20of%20Modi%2C%20the%20superstar%20of%20Indian%20politics%2C%20not%20to%20cater%20to%20the%20society%E2%80%99s%20spiritual%20stirrings%2C%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Looking%20Into%20Ayodhya's%20Ongoing%20Statue%20Politics%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Flooking-into-ayodhyas-ongoing-statue-politics%5C%22%3ELooking%20Into%20Ayodhya%E2%80%99s%20Ongoing%20Statue%20Politics%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPast%20prime%20ministers%2C%20too%2C%20visited%20temples%2C%20most%20notably%20Lal%20Bahadur%20Shastri%20and%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%20but%20never%20were%20posters%20bearing%20their%20pictures%20found%20in%20and%20around%20temples.%20This%20has%20changed%2C%20rues%20Tiwari%2C%20for%20on%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20recent%20visit%20to%20the%20Vishwanath%20Temple%2C%20a%20cutout%20of%20his%20was%20installed%20at%20its%20gates.%20Forget%20this%2C%20a%20religious%20rule%20will%20be%20violated%20by%20organising%20the%20ceremony%20of%20%3Cem%3Epran%20pratishtha%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20or%20giving%20life%20to%20the%20idol%2C%20in%20a%20temple%20still%20under%20construction%2C%20a%20point%20recently%20made%20by%20the%20four%20Shankaracharyas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECan%20I%20read%20the%20design%20behind%20the%20violation%20of%20the%20sacred%20rule%2C%20asks%20Tiwari.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20logical%20to%20complete%20the%20construction%20and%20inaugurate%20the%20temple%20on%20Ram%20Navami%2C%20the%20day%20he%20was%20born%2C%20which%20this%20year%20falls%20on%20April%2016.%20But%2C%20by%20then%2C%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20would%20be%20underway%20and%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20in%20place.%20%E2%80%9CModi%20wants%20to%20use%20Ram%20to%20gather%20votes.%20Power%20is%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Ram%2C%20his%20faith%2C%20his%20trade%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tiwari%20explains%20the%20hurry%20to%20organise%20the%20pran%20pratishtha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETiwari%20worries%20over%20the%20disregard%2C%20even%20contempt%2C%20shown%20in%20reimagining%20India%E2%80%99s%20sacred%20spaces%2C%20restructuring%20them%20in%20the%20manner%20of%20malls%2C%20where%20people%20go%20to%20make%20purchases%20and%20spend%20fun%20time%2C%20or%20turn%20them%20into%20tourist%20hubs.%20Both%20are%20attempts%20at%20commercially%20exploiting%20the%20sacred%2C%20not%20at%20evoking%20devotion%20for%20God%20among%20visitors.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20mall%2C%20not%20Ram%20Temple%20at%20Ayodhya.%20The%20first%20such%20mall%20to%20be%20built%20was%20the%20Kashi%20Vishwanath%20temple.%20The%20third%20one%20will%20come%20up%20at%20Mathura%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20540px)%2085vw%2C%20540px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21150816%2Fimage0-1.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22540%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21150816%2Fimage0-1.jpeg%20540w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F0