City%20of%20Ram%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20tussle%20between%20the%20temporal%20and%20the%20spiritual.%20The%20Sangh%20wants%20to%20acquire%20religious%20power%20in%20addition%20to%20its%20political%20heft.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20this%20happens%2C%20the%20Sangh%E2%80%99s%20control%20over%20our%20samaj%20would%20be%20complete%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20predicts.%20The%20Sangh%20seems%20set%20to%20achieve%20this%20goal%2C%20I%20said%2C%20given%20the%20public%20support%20for%20Modi.%20%E2%80%9CUntruth%20is%20always%20more%20alluring%20than%20truth%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tiwari%20responds.%20He%20lists%20the%2010%20values%20of%20Sanatan%20Dharma%2C%20such%20as%20to%20tell%20the%20truth%2C%20eschew%20arrogance%20and%20anger%2C%20cultivate%20forbearance%2C%20etc.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20these%20values%20are%20declining%2C%20none%20of%20these%20is%20embodied%20by%20Modi%2C%20who%20is%20turning%20us%20into%20fanatics%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETiwari%20recites%20verses%20predicting%20that%20Bhagwan%20would%20send%20his%20avatar%20whenever%20the%20fundamental%20values%20of%20Sanatan%20Dharma%20erode%20and%20the%20Hindu%20society%20deteriorates%20morally.%20Today%2C%20though%2C%20Tiwari%20will%20hope%20that%20God%20bestows%20wisdom%20on%20people%20so%20they%20can%20distinguish%20untruth%20from%20truth%2C%20and%20comprehend%20that%20the%20display%20of%20devotion%20for%20Ram%20today%20is%20a%20ploy%20to%20harvest%20votes%20%E2%80%93%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fajaz-ashraf%5C%22%3EAjaz%20Ashraf%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20Delhi-based%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705887047000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21150907%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-21-at-1.25.10-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpower-is-modis-ram-his-faith-his-trade%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Maha