or.%20There%20are%20two%20more%20upper%20sections%20left%20to%20restore%20and%20paint.%3Cp%3EMcKinley%20Manor%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20that's%20left%20are%20two%20upper%20sections%20on%20the%20exterior%20that%20need%20to%20be%20repainted%2C%20which%20Heemstra%20says%20she'll%20get%20to%20after%20winter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20lives%20about%2020%20minutes%20away%20and%20has%20no%20intention%20of%20moving%20into%20the%20house%20once%20it's%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20she%20plans%20to%20turn%20it%20into%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmckinleymanor.rentals%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evacation%20rental%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20she%20can%20host%20getaways%20for%20couples%20and%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERensselaer%20is%20about%20100%20miles%20south%20of%20Chicago%2C%20and%20a%20two-hour%20drive%20from%20Indianapolis.%20Vacationers%20often%20visit%20the%20Jasper%20County%20Fair%20or%20go%20on%20an%20art%20walk%20to%20explore%20public%20murals%20and%20sculptures%20around%20the%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20parlor%20room%20that's%20decorated%20with%20fancy%20furnishings%2C%20including%20a%20chandelier%2C%20patterned%20wallpaper%2C%20and%20wood%20furniture.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659cfc146979d73718218589%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20parlor%20is%20now%20a%20room%20where%20brides%20can%20get%20ready%20for%20their%20big%20day.%3Cp%3EMcKinley%20Manor%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHeemstra%20also%20sees%20the%20space%20as%20having%20potential%20for%20brides-to-be%20and%20has%20transformed%20the%20parlor%20into%20a%20dressing%20and%20make-up%20room%20filled%20with%20several%20antique%20vanities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20cool%20place%20downtown%20Rensselaer%20that's%20a%20wedding%20venue.%20It's%20an%20old%20building%2C%20but%20they%20don't%20real