20something%20new.%20I'm%20going%20to%20figure%20it%20out.%20It%20may%20not%20be%20perfect%20but%20I'll%20learn%20as%20I%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20Heemstra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22One%20of%20the%20bedrooms%20in%20the%20house.%20The%20room%20has%20a%20light%20blue%20color%20theme%20and%20features%20a%20bee%20wallpaper.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659cf9196979d7371821857e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20the%20bedrooms%20in%20the%20house.%3Cp%3EMcKinley%20Manor%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlready%20rented%20it%20once%20out%20before%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20the%20house%20isn't%20ready%20on%20the%20outside%2C%20Heemstra%20says%20that%20she's%20already%20rented%20the%20place%20out%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20for%20the%20fianc%C3%A9e%20of%20my%20friend's%20son%20to%20use%20while%20her%20bridal%20party%20got%20ready%20for%20their%20wedding%20in%20September%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20nice%20to%20be%20able%20to%20provide%20a%20beautiful%20spot%20for%20friends%20and%20a%20nice%20dry%20run%20to%20see%20how%20the%20space%20would%20work%20out%20for%20them.%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20bathroom%20on%20the%20second%20floor%20after%20restoration.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659cfd10ec62ab5daf81c5e5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20bathroom%20on%20the%20second%20floor.%3Cp%3EMcKinley%20Manor%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20effort%20it%20took%20to%20restore%20the%20manor%2C%20Heemstra%20says%20that%20she%20enjoyed%20the%20process%20so%20much%20that%20she's%20even%20got%20her%20next%20project%20lined%20up%20%E2%80%94%20the%20house%20next%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20like%20the%20idea%20that%20it's%20right%20next%20door.%20It%20was%20empty%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20like%20if%20I%20fix%20that%20up%2C%20it's%20only%20going%20to%20help%20my%20house%20with%20renting%20and%20value%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20her%20husband%20thought%20she%20was%20insane.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20like%2C%20'I%20can't%20believe%20you%20bought%20that.'%20And%20I'm%20like%2C%20'I%20know%2C%20I've%20lost%20my%20mind%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20showing%20the%20sink%20area%20and%20the%20shower%20area%20of%20the%20bathroom%20on%20the%20first%20floor.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659cfe98ec62ab5daf81c5f1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20bathroom%20on%20the%20first%20floor.%3Cp%3EMcKinley%20Manor%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHave%20a%20realistic%20timeline%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHeemstra%20has%20a%20piece%20of%20advice%20for%20those%20who%20are%20interested%20in%20restoring%20old%20houses%3A%20Be%20realistic%20about%20how%20long%20it'll%20take%20to%20complete%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20going%20to%20take%20longer%20than%20you%20think%20%E2%80%94%20I%20was%20so%20naive%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20would%20ask%2C%20'When%20is%20it%20going%20to%20be%20ready%3F'%20And%20in%20my%20mind%2C%20because%20of%20work%20that%20I've%20done%20before%20on%20our%20home%2C%20I%20was%20saying%20June%202021.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20would've%20meant%20that%20Heemstra%20completed%20the%20restoration%20project%20within%20a%20year%20of%20buying%20the%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223592%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20front%20porch%20of%20the%20house%20after%20restoration.%20There%20is%20a%20swinging%20seat%20where%20visitors%20can%20lounge.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%2