3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20first%20business%20%E2%80%94%20China%20Pages%20%E2%80%94%20failed%2C%20but%20he%20gathered%20a%20band%20of%2017%20friends%20in%201999%20to%20set%20up%20Alibaba.%20The%20site%20they%20launched%20allowed%20exporters%20to%20list%20their%20products%20directly%20on%20the%20platform%2C%20ushering%20China%20into%20the%20ecommerce%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20Ma%20is%20arguably%20the%20most%20successful%20internet%20entrepreneur%20of%20this%20generation%2C%20he%20started%20Alibaba%20with%20no%20knowledge%20of%20marketing%20or%20computers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20his%20start%20as%20a%20teacher%20taught%20him%20how%20to%20rally%20the%20troops%2C%20identify%20and%20cultivate%20talent%2C%20delegate%20work%2C%20and%20chart%20the%20direction%20for%20Alibaba%2C%20he%20said%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2018%2F09%2F20%2Fworking-as-a-teacher-taught-alibabas-jack-ma-this-business-skill.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDavos%20in%202018.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20was%20more%20of%20a%20teacher%20than%20a%20manager%2C%26quot%3B%20Brian%20Wong%2C%20the%2052nd%20employee%20of%20Alibaba%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20of%20Ma's%20management%20style.%20Wong%20spent%20nearly%20two%20decades%20at%20Alibaba%20over%20the%20course%20of%20three%20separate%20employment%20stints%20%E2%80%94%20from%201999%20to%202020.%20Most%20recently%2C%20he%20was%20the%20company's%20group%20vice%20president%20and%20remains%20an%20advisor%20to%20an%20Alibaba%20unit%20focused%20on%20education%20and%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJack%20does%20have%20an%20aspect%20of%20him%20that%20speaks%20his%20mind%2C%26quot%3B%20Wong%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20the%20most%20part%2C%20it's%20a%20positive%20asset%20in%20terms%20of%20how%20he%20has%20built%20the%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EJack%20Ma%202.0%3A%20An%20outgoing%20Big%20Tech%20exec%20%E2%80%94%20until%20he%20wasn't%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20internet%20entrepreneur%2C%20Ma%20was%20pivotal%20in%20steering%20the%20company%2C%20and%20his%20charisma%20corralled%20the%20support%20he%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20a%20master%20at%20communicating%20a%20shared%20aspiration%20that%20so%20many%20people%20can%20relate%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Wong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMa%20founded%20Alibaba.com%20in%20June%201999.%20In%20October%2C%20the%20company%20managed%20to%20raise%20%245%20million%20from%20Wall%20Street%20behemoth%20Goldman%20Sachs%20and%20another%20%2420%20million%20from%20Japanese%20tech%20investor%20SoftBank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20work%20culture%20at%20Alibaba%20was%20intense%2C%20but%20Ma%20was%20known%20for%20maintaining%20a%20sense%20of%20fun.%20In%20the%20early%202000s%2C%20when%20setting%20up%20the%20Taobao%20shopping%20platform%2C%20he%20made%20his%20team%20do%20headstands%20during%20breaks%20to%20boost%20their%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlibaba%20boomed%20through%20the%202000s%20in%20China.%20By%20the%20mid-2010s%2C%20Ma%20started%20dreaming%20beyond%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20Alibaba%20started%20trading%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falibaba-ipo-september-19-2014-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Stock%20Exchange%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Emaking%20Ma%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2014-12-11%2Fjack-ma-becomes-asia-s-richest-person-on-alibaba-surge%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erichest%20person%20in%20Asia%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20end%20of%20that%20year%20with%20an%20estimated%20%2425%20billion%20fortune.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20I'm%20thinking%20about%20is%20how%20we%20can%20make%20Alibaba%20a%20platform%20for%20global%20small%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20Ma%20told%20journalist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Fwhy-alibabas-jack-ma-isnt-scared-of-chinas-slowdown%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECharlie%20Rose%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20in%20Da