Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fobituaries-people-news%2Fjohn-hamlin-dead-oscars-telecasts-1235881021%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fobituaries-people-news%2Fjohn-hamlin-dead-oscars-telecasts-1235881021%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22An%20Alabama%20prisoner%20will%20soon%20become%20the%20first%20in%20the%20US%20to%20be%20executed%20by%20nitrogen%20gas.%20Veterinarians%20won't%20even%20use%20the%20method%20on%20most%20animals.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alabama's%20lethal%20injection%20chamber%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F58487a4aba6eb61c008b80f5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221103%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlabama's%20lethal%20injection%20chamber%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAn%20Alabama%20prisoner%20is%20about%20to%20undergo%20an%20experimental%20execution%20using%20nitrogen%20gas%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20inmate's%20attorney%20told%20a%20federal%20appeals%20court%20on%20Friday%20it%20constitutes%20cruel%20and%20unusual%20punishment.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEven%20veterinarians%20refrain%20from%20using%20nitrogen%20gas%20in%20euthanasias%20for%20most%20animals.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Alabama%20prisoner%20is%20scheduled%20to%20be%20executed%20by%20nitrogen%20gas%20on%20Tuesday%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0an%20experimental%20form%20of%20capital%20punishment%20that%20has%20prompted%20a%20global%20outcry%20from%20human%20rights%20organizations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKenneth%20Eugene%20Smith%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falabama-plans-execution-kenneth-smith-gas-warning-others-hurt-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurvived%20a%20lethal%20injection%20attempt%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20September%202022%2C%20when%20officials%20from%20Alabama's%20Department%20of%20Corrections%20tried%20and%20failed%20for%20four%20hours%20to%20find%20a%20vein%20to%20insert%20an%20IV%20line.%20A%20federal%20judge%20then%20ruled%20that%20an%20execution%20by%20nitrogen%20hypoxia%20can%20go%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20High%20Commissioner%20for%20Human%20Rights%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohchr.org%2Fen%2Fpress-briefing-notes%2F2024%2F01%2Fus-alarm-over-imminent-execution-alabama%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecriticized%20the%20planned%20execution%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20saying%20it%20violates%20international%20human%20rights%20treaties%2C%20including%20the%20prohibition%20on%20%26quot%3Btorture%20or%20other%20cruel%2C%20inhuman%2C%20or%20degrading%20treatment%20or%20punishment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECritics%20have%20also%20pointed%20to%20the%20American%20Veterinary%20Medical%20Association's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.avma.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2020-02%2FGuidelines-on-Euthanasia-2020.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2020%20euthanasia%20guidelines%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20say%20nitrogen%20hypoxia%20creates%20an%20%26quot%3Banoxic%20environment%20that%20is%20distressing%20for%20some%20species.%26quot%3B%20The%20AVMA%20now%20says%20the%20gas%20can%20be%20used%20under%20certain%20conditions%20for%20chickens%2C%20turkeys%2C%20and%20pigs%2C%20but%20is%20deemed%20%26quot%3Bunacceptable%26quot%3B%20for%20other%20mammals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20a%20federal%20appeals%20court%20heard%20arguments%20from%20Smith's%20attorney%20in%20a%20last-minute%20effort%20to%20block%20the%20execution%2C%20saying%20a%20second%20execution%20attempt%20would%20constitute%20cruel%20and%20unusual%20punishment.%20Alabama's%20solicitor%20general%20argued%20that%20the%20state%20has%20%26quot%3Badopted%20the%20most%20painless%20and%20humane%20method%20of%20execution%20known%20to%20man%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Falabama-execution-nitrogen-gas-hypoxia-f8b818b74542783612a0574de65cc0c2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20Associated%20Press%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20nitrogen%20hypoxia%20execution%20method%2C%20which%20remains%20untested%2C%20involves%20a%20mask%20being%20fitted%20to%20the%20prisoner's%20face%2C%20which%20pipes%20in%20nitrogen%20gas.%20But%20Smith's%20lawyer%20has%20argued%20there%20is%20a%20risk%20that%20the%20mask's%20seal%20could%20leak%20in%20oxygen%2C%20causing%20a%20prolonged%20and%20terrifying%20execution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFederal%20appeals%20judges%20on%20Friday%20also%20asked%20what%20would%20happen%20if%20Smith%20vomited%20into%20the%20mask%20%E2%80%94%20to%20which%20Alabama's%20solicitor%20general%20responded%20that%20the%20state%20would%20not%20stop%20the%20nitrogen%20gas%20once%20it%20began%20flowing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20he%20vomits%20during%20the%20execution%20with%20the%20mask%20on%2C%20you're%20telling%20me%20that%20the%20state%20will%20not%20stop%20the%20execution%2C%20they%20will%20permit%20him%20to%20choke%20on%20his%20vomit%3F%26quot%3B%20one%20judge%20asked%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Associated%20Press.%20The%20solicitor%20general%20replied%20that%20the%20risk%20of%20vomiting%20was%20low%20and%20that%20Smith%20would%20be%20unconscious%20almost%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%20was%20convicted%20of%20the%20brutal%20murder-for-hire%20scheme%20against%20Elizabeth%20Sennett%20in%201988.%20Smith%20and%20another%20man%20each%20accepted%20%241%2C000%20from%20Sennett's%20husband%2C%20a%20preacher%20who%20had%20taken%20out%20an%20insurance%20policy%20on%20his%20wife%20and%20died%20by%20suicide%20before%20he%20could%20be%20criminally%20charged%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.al.com%2Fnews%2F2022%2F11%2Fformer-sheriff-recalls-womans-horrific-murder-for-hire-by-pastor-as-alabama-prepares-execution.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSennett%2520claimed%2520he%2520found%2520his%2Ca%2520home%2520invasion%2520and%2520burglary.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20AL.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Authorities%20said%20Sennett%20had%20been%20sta