0it%20said%20were%20%26quot%3Bplanned%20attacks%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20convoys%20of%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20in%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20late-night%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Congress%20general%20secretary%2C%20organisation%2C%20K%20C%20Venugopal%20alleged%20that%20since%20the%20yatra's%20entry%20in%20Assam%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20corrupt%20CM%20in%20India%20has%20been%20carrying%20out%20relentless%20attacks%20on%20our%20convoys%2C%20properties%20and%20leaders%20using%20his%20goons.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20matter%20that%20every%20Indian%20must%20take%20seriously%2C%20because%20it%20exposes%20the%20BJP's%20fascism%20and%20hooliganism.%20All%20across%20India%2C%20PCCs%20and%20DCCs%20are%20instructed%20to%20hold%20large%20scale%20protests%20tomorrow%20evening%20and%20exposing%20how%20the%20Modi-led%20BJP%20is%20killing%20democracy%20in%20Assam%20through%20their%20corrupt%20CM%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Venugopal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ESince%20our%20entry%20in%20Assam%2C%20the%20most%20corrupt%20CM%20in%20India%20has%20been%20carrying%20out%20relentless%20attacks%20on%20our%20convoys%2C%20properties%20and%20leaders%20using%20his%20goons.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThis%20is%20a%20matter%20that%20every%20Indian%20must%20take%20seriously%2C%20because%20it%20exposes%20the%20BJP's%20fascism%20and%20hooliganism.%20All%20across%20India%2C%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FHiIWCD5jaU%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FHiIWCD5jaU%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20K%20C%20Venugopal%20(%40kcvenugopalmp)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkcvenugopalmp%2Fstatus%2F1749130464252907989%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2021%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20fight%20for%20justice%20-%20social%2C%20economic%2C%20and%20political%20-%20will%20continue%20undeterred!%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2