ed%20not%20only%20in%20and%20around%20the%20temple%20area%20but%20also%20all%20over%20Ayodhya%20to%20enable%20everyone%20to%20witness%20the%20spectacle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHuge%20screens%20have%20also%20been%20installed%20in%20a%20specially%20created%20media%20centre%20as%20well%20as%20along%20Ram%20ki%20Pairi%20on%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20Sarayu%20river%2C%20where%20spaces%20have%20been%20allotted%20to%20different%20TV%20and%20digital%20media%20channels.%20Only%20Doordarshan%20and%20ANI%20have%20been%20allowed%20inside%20the%20main%20venue%20at%20the%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20entire%20town%20is%20lit%20up%20with%20glowing%20colours%2C%20while%20Ram%20Bhajans%20are%20reverberating%20from%20loud%20speakers%20installed%20at%20intermittent%20lamp%20posts.%20The%2050-minute%20pran%20pratishtha%20will%20commence%20at%2012%3A05%20pm%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705845232000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21191409%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-21-at-4.19.49-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffinal-touches-in-progress-ahead-of-the-big-show-in-ayodhya-tomorrow%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20heavy%20security%20blanket%20is%20in%20place%2C%20and%20all%20entry%20points%20into%20the%20city%20have%20been%20sealed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffinal-touches-in-progress-ahead-of-the-big-show-in-ayodhya-tomorrow%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20World%20with%20Yalda%20Hakim%20-%20Sky%20News%20launches%20new%20foreign%20affairs%20show%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705845000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F01%2F768x432%2Fskynews-the-world-yada-hakim_6426878.jpg%3F20240119185125%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fsky-news-launches-new-foreign-affairs-show-t