rge%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CNowadays%20in%20Assam%2C%20those%20who%20left%20us%20and%20joined%20BJP%20are%20the%20%E2%80%98new%20converted%20CMs%E2%80%99.%20They%20are%20threatening%20us.%20BJP%20people%20also%20attacked%20the%20Yatra%20and%20broke%20the%20glass%20panes%20of%20the%20vehicles.%20Poster%2FBanner%20also%20torn.%20If%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20bow%20before%20the%20British%2C%20then%20how%20will%20we%20bow%20before%20the%20BJP%3F%20The%20CM%20here%20forgets%20that%20he%20himself%20is%20accused%20of%20countless%20scams%2C%20cases%20are%20registered%20under%20many%20sections.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CRahul%20Ji%20rightly%20said%20that%20the%20CM%20of%20Assam%20is%20the%20most%20corrupt%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20the%20country.%20If%20today%20they%20are%20being%20honest%20and%20clean%2C%20then%20it%20is%20only%20because%20of%20the%20wonder%20of%20Modi%20ji%20and%20Amit%20Shah%20ji%E2%80%99s%20washing%20machine.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Assam%20CM%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20has%20gone%20onto%20say%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20should%20avoid%20visiting%20Batadrawa%20Than%2C%20the%20birthplace%20of%20Vaishnavite%20saint%20Srimanta%20Sankardeva%2C%20at%20the%20same%20time%20as%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%20But%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fassam%2Frahul-to-visit-assamese-icon-sankardevas-birthplace-on-jan-22-as-scheduled-congress-2858237%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20Congress%20general%20secretary%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20maintained%20that%20Gandhi%20will%20visit%20the%20Than%20in%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20Nagaon%20district%20as%20planned%20and%20urged%20that%20%E2%80%98no%20politics%20should%20be%20done%20over%20it%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20route%20of%20the%20Yatra%20was%20fixed%20three%20to%20four%20weeks%20before%20and%20as%20per%20the%20schedule%2C%20we%20will%20be%20in%20Nagaon%20on%20January%2022%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ramesh%2C%20who%20is%20with%20the%20Yatra%2C%20said%20at%20the%20press%20conference%20here%20on%20the%20way%20to%20the%20central%20Assam%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20think%20it%20is%20imperative%20that%20we%20visit%20Batadrawa%20Than%20as%20we%20are%20passing%20through%20Nagaon.%20It%20is%20the%20birthplace%20of%20the%20great%20social%20reformer%20Srimanta%20Sankardeva%2C%20whose%20life%20continues%20to%20inspire%20crores%20of%20people%20even%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20should%20not%20have%20been%20any%20dispute%20over%20it.%20No%20politics%20should%20be%20done%20over%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Congress%20leader%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Gandhi%20will%20visit%20the%20Than%20on%20Monday%20morning%20and%20then%20commence%20the%20day%E2%80%99s%20Yatra%2C%20during%20which%20he%20will%20travel%20through%20Morigaon%20district%20before%20entering%20neighbouring%20Meghalaya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Yatra%20is%20set%20to%20return%20to%20Assam%20after%20a%20short%20trip%20in%20the%20neighbouring%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FPTI_News%2Fstatus%2F1748935650038948311%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3EPTI%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20when%20asked%20why%20the%20Assam%20chief%20minister%20was%20edgy%20and%20prickly%20about%20the%20Yatra%20in%20its%20east%20to%20west%20journey%2C%20after%20having%20already%20logged%20an%20unprecedented%20south%20to%20north%20trip%20last%20year%2C%20Gandhi%20repeated%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20(BJP)%20are%20afraid%2C%20the%20(Assam)%20CM%20(Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma)%20is%20afraid%2C%20and%20he%20is%20a%20corrupt%20person.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Assam%20segment%20of%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20is%20from%20January%2018%20to%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705843687000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21185641%2FGEXZJsOWEAAun8w.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2