Saturday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20flight%20was%20a%20charter%20ambulance%20from%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Findia%2Ft-18996071%5C%22%3EIndia%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0via%20Uzbekistan%20to%20Moscow%20on%20a%20French-made%20Dassault%20Falcon%2010%20jet%20manufactured%20in%201978%2C%20they%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20It%20had%20refueled%20in%20India%20having%20come%20from%20Thailand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20civil%20aviation%20authority%20clarified%20that%20the%20aircraft%20was%20not%20a%20scheduled%20commercial%20flight%20or%20an%20Indian%20chartered%20plane%20and%20that%20they%20awaited%20more%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20aircraft%20is%20said%20to%20have%20crashed%20in%20the%20Badakhshan%20province%20which%20borders%20China%2C%20Tajikistan%2C%20and%20Pakistan.%20However%2C%20the%20exact%20location%20of%20the%20crash%20is%20still%20unknown%2C%20news%20agency%20AFP%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20plane%20has%20crashed%20but%20the%20location%20is%20not%20known%20yet.%20We%20have%20sent%20teams%20but%20they%20have%20not%20arrived%20yet%2C%E2%80%9D%20Zabihullah%20Amiri%2C%20head%20of%20the%20provincial%20information%20department%20said%20without%20giving%20further%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20informed%20by%20local%20people%20in%20the%20morning.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20province%20is%20home%20to%20part%20of%20the%20Hindu%20Kush%20mountain%20range%20and%20Afghanistan%E2%80%99s%20highest%20peak%2C%20Mount%20Noshaq%2C%20at%207%2C492%20meters%20(24%2C580%20feet)%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Frussian-plane-crashes-in-northeastern-afghanistan-mountains%2Fa-68044457%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Ftop-stories%2Fs-9097%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705842786000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcd