0You%20ought%20to%20drown%20in%20shame%20each%20time%20you%20call%20out%20for%20this%20%E2%80%9CUnity%E2%80%9D%20of%20yours.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20if%20you%20lot%20are%20weirdly%20self-obsessed%20or%20%E2%80%A6%20or%20%E2%80%A6%20just%20plain%20impotent!%20If%20there%E2%80%99s%20any%20blood%20in%20your%20biceps%2C%20will%20it%20only%20stir%20when%20these%20Muslims%20enter%20your%20own%20homes%2C%20and%20your%20mothers%20and%20sisters%20are%20vio%E2%80%94%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20299px)%2085vw%2C%20299px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21164555%2FScreenshot-2024-01-21-at-4.45.32-PM-203x300.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22299%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21164555%2FScreenshot-2024-01-21-at-4.45.32-PM-203x300.png%20203w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21164555%2FScreenshot-2024-01-21-at-4.45.32-PM.png%20682w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693894%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22442%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENanak%20Singh%2C%3Cbr%3EA%20Game%20of%20Fire%2C%3Cbr%3EHarperCollins%20India%20(2024)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20young%20man%E2%80%99s%20face%20was%20flushed%2C%20each%20sentence%20exploding%20from%20his%20lips%20like%20molten%20lava%20from%20a%20volcanic%20eruption%2C%20his%20words%20crashing%20into%20the%20audience%20with%20the%20seismic%20force%20of%20tectonic%20plates.%20There%20was%20a%20stunned%20silence%20in%20the%20room%2C%20followed%20soon%20by%20a%20flicker%20of%20resentment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20speaker%20was%20a%20young%20man%20of%20about%20twenty-two%20or%20twenty%20three%2C%20possibly%20a%20college%20student%20if%20one%20went%20by%20his%20attire.%20They%20were%20inside%20a%20nondescript%20house%20located%20approximately%20midway%20between%20the%20Putlighar%20crossing%20and%20Khalsa%20College%20on%20the%20Grand%20Trunk%20Road%20as%20it%20traversed%20through%20Amritsar.%20A%20dozen%20young%20men%20sat%20around%20a%20table%20in%20a%20largish%20room%20in%20that%20house%E2%80%94six%20were%20Sikh%2C%20four%20Hindu%20and%20two%20Muslim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20an%20evening%20in%20early%20March.%20The%20festival%20of%20Holi%20was%20around%20the%20corner%2C%20meaning%20that%20the%20winds%20had%20strengthened%20over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20days%2C%20enveloping%20people%20in%20the%20streets%20and%20bazaars%20in%20clouds%20of%20dust.%20The%20young%20men%20who%20were%20sitting%20around%20the%20table%20had%20set%20up%20their%20Unity%20Council%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20back.%20The%20Council%20had%20started%20off%20with%20a%20fair%20bit%20of%20enthusiasm.%20Its%20first%20couple%20of%20meetings%20were%20attended%20by%20almost%20a%20hundred%20members%2C%20but%20those%20numbers%20had%20dwindled%20rapidly%20to%20the%20dozen%20present%20this%20evening.%20And%20if%20the%20fireworks%20on%20display%20today%20were%20any%20indication%2C%20it%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20long%20before%20the%20Council%E2%80%99s%20last%20rites%20were%20performed%20without%20much%20fanfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20young%20man%E2%80%99s%20fiery%20discourse%20had%20left%20the%20others%20speechless%2C%20their%20faces%20reflecting%20a%20curious%20array%20of%20expressions%20ranging%20from%20fear%20and%20guilt%20to%20anger%20and%20indignation.%20Emotions%20were%20rising%20around%20the%20table%20as%20he%20continued%20his%20diatribe%20when%20a%20young%20Sikh%2C%20who%20was%20sitting%20next%20to%20the%20speaker%2C%20quickly%20rose%20from%20his%20chair.%20In%20a%20flash%2C%20his%20right%20hand%20moved%20to%20cover%20the%20speaker%E2%80%99s%20mouth%20and%20prevent%20him%20from%20causing%20further%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Sudharshan!%E2%80%99%20the%20Sikh%20fumed.%20%E2%80%98Have%20you%20lost%20your%20senses%3F%20You%20forget%20that%20we%20are%20members%20of%20the%20Unity%20Council%20who%E2%80%99ve%20pledged%20to%20dowse%20the%20communal%20fire%2C%20not%20fan%20its%20flames%20through%20tirades%20like%20these.%20The%20terrible%20things%20that%20you%E2%80%99ve%20pointed%20out%20may%20well%20be%20true.%20But%20does%20that%20mean%20that%20we%20should%20also%20allow%20ourselves%20to%20be%20swept%20into%20this%20flood%20of%20communal%20hatred%20instead%20of%20trying%20to%20save%20others%2C%20as%20we%20had%20once%E2%80%94%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECutting%20him%20off%20mid-sentence%2C%20Sudarshan%20continued%20in%20the%20same%20blistering%20voice%2C%20%E2%80%98You%E2%80%99d%20better%20understand%2C%20Satnam%2C%20that%20the%20lofty%20purpose%20that%20brought%20us%20together%20is%20now%20a%20mirage.%20You%20won%E2%80%99t%20reach%20your%20goal%20even%20if%20you%20keep%20trying%20till%20the%20end%20of%20time.%20Mark%20my%20words%2C%20Satnam.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20reached%20a%20stage%20where%20we%20must%20fight%20fire%20with%20fire.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20heard%20the%20blood-curdling%20accounts%20of%20refugees%20fleeing%20the%20Frontier%20Province%20and%20my%20heart%20bleeds%20from%20a%20thousand%20cuts.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20taken%20a%20solemn%20vow%20that%20I%E2%80%99ll%20avenge%20the%20death%20of%20each%20one%20of%20my%20fellows%20by%20killing%20at%20least%20four%20of%20theirs.%20I%20haven%E2%80%99t%20come%20here%20today%20to%20attend%20this%20council%20of%20yours.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20come%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20its%20membership%20for%20good.%20Here%20you%20go!%E2%80%99%20And%2C%20so%20saying%2C%20he%20reached%20inside%20his%20jacket%20to%20withdraw%20a%20piece%20of%20folded%20paper%20and%20flung%20it%20at%20Satnam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESatnam%20picked%20up%20the%20resignation%20letter%20and%20put%20it%20on%20the%20table%20without%20reading%20it.%20At%20the%20moment%2C%20he%20was%20more%20worried%20that%20today%E2%80%99s%20meeting%20would%20end%20in%20bloodshed.%20The%20two%20Muslim%20members%20sat%20across%20the%20table%20from%20him%2C%20their%20heads%20were%20lowered%20in%20anxiety%20even%20as%20they%20sensed%20the%20pointed%20gaze%20of%20the%20Hindus%20and%20Sikhs%20upon%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20young%20Hindu%20who%20was%20seated%20beside%20them%20piped%20up%2C%20%E2%80%98Sardar%20Satnam%20Singh%20ji%2C%20forgive%20me%2C%20but%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20entirely%20dismiss%20Sudarshan%E2%80%99s%20comments.%20We%20need%20to%20reflect%20deeply%20on%20what%20he%20has%20said.%20Frankly%2C%20I%20also%20feel%20that%20this%20Unity%20Council%20has%20become%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20farce.%20The%20disease%20of%20communal%20hatred%20has%20now%20spread%20throughout%20our%20body%3B%20the%20patient%20is%20in%20critical%20condition%20and%20the%20prescriptions%20coming%20out%20of%20this%20Unity%20Council%20will%20do%20nothing%20to%20cure%20him.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20be%20honest%20for%20a%20moment.%20Over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20months%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20shouted%20ourselves%20hoarse%20calling%20for%20communal%20amity%2C%20printed%20and%20distributed%20thousands%20of%20pamphlets%2C%20published%20articles%20in%20major%20newspapers%2C%20stuck%20giant%20posters%20and%20given%20speeches%E2%80%94but%20has%20any%20of%20it%20resulted%20in%20something%20tangible%3F%20Have%20our%20efforts%20reduced%20the%20level%20of%20communal%20hatred%3F%20Not%20at%20all.%20If%20anything%2C%20it%20continues%20to%20increase%20with%20each%20passing%20day.%20And%20you%20are%20also%20aware%20of%20another%20grim%20reality.%20We%20are%20all%20at%20the%20mercy%20of%20Amritsar%E2%80%99s%20Muslim-dominated%20police%20force%E2%80%94the%20same%20people%20who%20are%20inciting%20their%20Muslim%20brethren%20to%20launch%20a%20jihad%20against%20their%20Hindu%20and%20Sikh%20neighbours%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Freview-nanak-singh-khoon-de-sohile%5C%22%3EReview%3A%20The%20Pristine%20Home%20and%20Partition%20as%20Violence%20in%20Nanak%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Khoon%20de%20Sohile%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98And%20remember%20this%2C%E2%80%99%20chimed%20in%20another%20young%20Hindu%2C%20his%20western%20attire%20topped%20up%20with%20a%20very%20English-looking%20cap.%20%E2%80%98You%20can%20keep%20trying%20till%20the%20end%20of%20time%2C%20but%20there%20is%20absolutely%20no%20chance%20that%20your%20prescription%20will%20work.%20This%20council%20has%20now%20been%20around%20for%20over%20two%20months.%20Is%20there%20a%20single%20achievement%20that%20we%20can%20highlight%2C%20apart%20from%20wasting%20people%E2%80%99s%20time%20with%20these%20pointless%20meetings%20at%20one%20location%20or%20another%3F%20From%20the%20reports%20that%20I%20read%20in%20the%20newspapers%2C%20it%20is%20quite%20clear%20that%20the%20forbearance%20of%20Hindus%20and%20Sikhs%20is%20being%20exploited%20by%20the%20Muslims%20and%20they%20are%20becoming%20more%20aggressive%20by%20the%20day.%20The%20destruction%20wrought%20in%20Hazara%20and%20Pothohar%20is%20a%20living%20example%20of%20this%20trend.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98But%20Mr%20Kumar!%E2%80%99%20Satnam%20turned%20around%20to%20address%20him.%20%E2%80%98In%20your%20opinion%2C%20what%20is%20the%20reason%20for%20this%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKumar%20leaned%20forward%20towards%20Satnam%20as%20he%20spoke%2C%20%E2%80%98The%20reason%20is%20that%20right%20now%2C%20the%20fanaticism%20of%20the%20Muslims%20has%20crossed%20all%20limits.%20You%20can%20pull%20out%20the%20press%20clippings%20for%20the%20last%20one%20month%20and%20read%20about%20the%20violence%20in%20Hazara%20and%20Pothohar.%20I%20am%20sure%20that%20after%20reading%20them%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20also%20agree%20that%20this%20Unity%20Council%20of%20yours%20is%20utterly%20pointless.%20The%20other%20side%20is%20hurling%20bricks%20at%20you%20and%20you%20want%20to%20respond%20by%20throwing%20flowers%20at%20them%3F%20The%20sheer%20absurdity%20of%20your%20ideals!%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98So%2C%20does%20this%20mean%20that%E2%80%A6%E2%80%99%20the%20Muslim%20named%20Ishaaq%20who%20was%20sitting%20three%20chairs%20away%20from%20Kumar%20interjected%2C%20%E2%80%98it%20must%20be%20an%20eye%20for%20an%20eye%2C%20that%20each%20action%20must%20be%20followed%20by%20a%20stronger%20reaction%3F%20If%20you%20think%20that%20approach%20is%20going%20to%20help%20our%20city%20or%20our%20nation%2C%20then%20I%20have%20to%20agree%20that%20this%20council%20of%20ours%20can%20offer%20no%20solution.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Well%2C%20if%20I%20can%20be%20honest%E2%80%A6%E2%80%99%20Tarlochan%20Singh%20spoke%20from%20the%20seat%20on%20Satnam%E2%80%99s%20left.%20%E2%80%98The%20fact%20is%20that%20this%20council%20has%20automatically%20ceased%20to%20exist%20because%20of%20the%20lack%20of%20quorum%20in%20the%20last%20few%20meetings.%20A%20membership%20of%20around%20a%20hundred%20and%20the%20record%20shows%20attendance%20of%20barely%20a%20dozen!%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESalmani%2C%20who%20was%20sitting%20next%20to%20Ishaaq%2C%20tried%20to%20get%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20others%20as%20he%20cleared%20his%20throat%20to%20speak%2C%20%E2%80%98We%20set%20up%20this%20council%20to%20try%20and%20keep%20religious%20bigotry%20at%20bay%2C%20but%20it%20seems%20to%20me%20that%20maybe%2090%20or%2095%20per%20cent%20of%20our%20own%20council%20are%20falling%20prey%20to%20the%20same%20bigotry.%20The%20heated%20address%20and%20resignation%20letter%20of%20a%20member%20like%20Sudarshan%20has%20given%20us%20ample%20evidence%20of%20this.%E2%80%99%3Cbr%3E%5CnSudarshan%20was%20still%20seething%20when%20he%20heard%20the%20comment%20and%20launched%20himself%20at%20Salmani%20with%20the%20same%20venom.%20%E2%80%98Let%20me%20make%20my%20position%20absolutely%20clear%20once%20again%20to%20Mr%20Salmani.%20If%20getting%20influenced%20by%20the%20savage%20killings%20of%20my%20brothers%20and%20the%20public%20dishonour%20of%20my%20sisters%20is%20bigotry%2C%20so%20be%20it.%20I%20am%20not%20at%20all%20embarrassed%20for%20failing%20your%20touchstone.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98In%20that%20case%2C%20you%E2%80%99d%20better%20be%20prepared%2C%20Mr%20Sudarshan%2C%E2%80%99%20Salmani%20replied%20with%20rising%20anger.%20%E2%80%98Go%20ahead%20and%20seek%20your%20revenge%20wherever%20you%20want%2C%20but%20get%20ready%20to%20face%20the%20reprisals%20too.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98You%20aren%E2%80%99t%20going%20to%20scare%20us%20with%20such%20threats%2C%20Mr%20Salmani.%20The%20writing%20on%20the%20wall%20is%20clear.%20Hindus%20and%20Sikhs%20will%20have%20to%20sort%20out%20the%20Muslims%20and%20bring%20this%20matter%20to%20a%20definitive%20close.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Looks%20like%20you%20are%20challenging%20the%20Muslims%20to%20step%20up%20and%20fight%20even%20as%20you%20sit%20in%20this%20council%2C%E2%80%99%20Ishaaq%20rose%20indignantly.%20An%20animated%20chatter%20went%20around%20the%20table%2C%20forcing%20Satnam%20to%20get%20up%20from%20the%20table.%20He%20urged%20them%20to%20be%20quiet%20for%20a%20minute%20as%20he%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENanak%20Singh%C2%A0(1897%E2%80%931971)%20is%20widely%20regarded%20as%20the%20father%20of%20the%20Punjabi%20novel.%20Despite%20little%20formal%20education%20beyond%20the%20fourth%20grade%2C%20he%20wrote%20an%20astounding%20fifty-nine%20books%2C%20which%20included%20thirty-eight%20novels%20and%20an%20assortment%20of%20plays%2C%20short%20stories%2C%20poems%2C%20essays%2C%20and%20even%C2%A0a%C2%A0set%20of%20translations.%20He%20received%20the%20Sahitya%20Akademi%20Award%20in%201962%20for%C2%A0Ik%20Mian%20Do%20Talwaraan.%20His%20novel%C2%A0Pavitra%20Paapi%C2%A0was%20made%20into%C2%A0a%C2%A0film%20in%201968%2C%20while%C2%A0Chitta%20Lahu%C2%A0was%20translated%20into%20the%20Russian%20by%20Natasha%20Tolstoy.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENavdeep%20Suri%C2%A0is%C2%A0a%C2%A0former%20diplomat%20who%20has%20served%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20diplomatic%20missions%20in%20Washington%2C%20D.C.%20and%20London.%20He%20was%20India%E2%80%99s%20Ambassador%20to%20Egypt%20and%20UAE%2C%20High%20Commissioner%20to%20Australia%2C%20and%20Consul%20General%20in%20Johannesburg.%20He%20has%20been%20striving%20to%20preserve%20the%20legacy%20of%20his%20grandfather%20Nanak%20Singh%20and%20to%20bring%20his%20works%20to%C2%A0a%C2%A0wider%20audience.%20He%20has%20translated%20into%20English%20the%20classic%201930s%20Punjabi%20novels%C2%A0Pavitra%20Paapi%C2%A0(The%20Watchmaker)%20and%C2%A0Adh%20Khidya%20Phul%C2%A0(A%C2%A0Life%20Incomplete).%20His%20translation%20of%20Nanak%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20lost%20poem%C2%A0Khooni%20Vaisakhi%C2%A0was%20published%20in%202019%20and%20of%20the%20novel%C2%A0Khoon%20de%20Sohile%C2%A0(Hymns%20in%20Blood)%20in%202022.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705837174000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F08%2F19113915%2Fpic-3-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fthe-story-of-a-city-in-turmoil-and-a-message-of-communal-harmony-relevant-76-years-later%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nanak%20Singh's%20A%20Game%20of%20Fire%20is%20the%20sequel%20to%20his%20novel%20Hymns%20of%20Blood%20originally%20published%20in%20Punjabi%20and%20translated%20by%20his%20grandson%20Navdeep%20Suri.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fthe-story-of-a-city-in-turmoil-and-a-message-of-communal-harmony-relevant-76-years-later%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Budget%202024-25%3A%20Govt%20may%20increase%20capex%20to%20propel%20economic%20growth%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705836287000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-11%2F23%2Ffull%2F1700760561-3211.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fbudget%2Fnews%2Fbudget-2024-25-govt-likely-to-do-heavy-lifting-capex-to-increase-1