gh%20the%20material%20provided%20by%20Puranic%20legends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPauranic%20plays%20have%20come%20to%20mean%20plays%20about%20Rama%20and%20Krishna%2C%20which%20involve%20bhakti.%20But%20there%20is%20so%20much%20else%20that%20is%20from%20the%20Puranas%2C%20there%20are%20such%20marvellous%20stories%2C%20which%20don%E2%80%99t%20involve%20the%20gods%20at%20all.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20involve%20Rama%20or%20Krishna.%20In%20the%20Vedas%20you%20find%20something%2C%20in%20the%20Upanishads%20you%20find%20them.%20%5B%3Cem%3EAgni%20Mattu%20Mal%C3%A9%3C%2Fem%3E%5D%20is%20about%20a%20story%20from%20the%20Mahabharata%2C%20but%20which%20does%20not%20involve%20Rama%2C%20Krishna%20or%20any%20of%20the%20gods.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20Vedic%20tale.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20playwriting%20was%20concerned%2C%20he%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20story%20may%20be%20from%20the%20past.%20But%20the%20play%20must%20be%20about%20the%20present%E2%80%A6%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20deliberately%20try%20to%20make%20it%20a%20contemporary%20subject.%20If%20I%20have%20a%20contemporary%20consciousness%2C%20it%20will%20become%20modern%20because%20I%20am%20a%20modern%20writer%20writing%20about%20it%2C%20you%20see.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20the%20Mahabharata%20was%20not%20just%20a%20store%20of%20minor%20legends%20from%20which%20to%20elicit%20modern%20literature.%20Karnad%20had%20an%20abiding%2C%20overarching%20interest%20in%20the%20central%20story%20of%20the%20Mahabharata%20war%20%E2%80%94%20and%20its%20potency%20in%20Indian%20history%20and%20society%2C%20even%20in%20the%20present%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20flat%20in%20Bombay%2C%20where%20he%20lived%20with%20his%20family%20through%20the%201980s%2C%20he%20kept%20a%2014-volume%20edition%20of%20the%20Mahabharata%20in%20Sanskrit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20538px)%2085vw%2C%20538px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%