0that%20struck%20us%20was%20to%20promote%20tourism%20in%20the%20village.%20Increased%20tourism%20not%20only%20benefits%20the%20village%20directly%20but%20also%20contributes%20to%20the%20growth%20of%20local%20businesses%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20opines.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20my%20friends%20from%20Shilling%20who%20was%20in%20the%20tourism%20industry%20was%20the%20one%20who%20gave%20us%20the%20courage%20to%20take%20the%20leap.%20He%20helped%20us%20with%20setting%20up%20the%20property%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20society%E2%80%99s%20umbrella%2C%20Bisharlang%20initiated%20Mawlyngbna%20Traveller%E2%80%99s%20Nest%2C%20a%20unique%20combination%20of%20a%20homestay%20and%20camping%20site%20for%20tourists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20so%20much%20to%20see%20and%20explore%20in%20the%20area%20but%20most%20people%20flock%20to%20the%20mainstream%20hills%20station.%20We%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20that%20attracts%20tourists%20and%20this%20is%20how%20the%20idea%20of%20an%20adventure%20camp%20came%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnder%20the%20society%2C%20we%20are%20240%20members%20who%20work%20in%20bringing%20new%20job%20avenues%20for%20people.%20Through%20the%20homestay%20and%20camp%20alone%2C%20we%20have%20trained%2040%20people%20in%20different%20tasks%20like%20hospitality%2C%20housekeeping%20and%20trek%20guiding%20and%20given%20them%20jobs%20at%20the%20homestay%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAdventure%2C%20nature%20and%20culture%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20initial%20response%20of%20the%20tourists%2C%20Bishar%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20back%20in%202014%2C%20while%20it%20was%20a%20good%20dream%2C%20the%20initial%20response%20was%20not%20how%20we%20expected%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max