%20and%20not%20many%20producers%20offer%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20millet%20options.%20Recognising%20this%20gap%2C%20I%20founded%20my%20own%20millet%20startup%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sai%20Krishna%20Popuri%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Health%20Sutra%2C%20as%20shared%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESai%2C%20the%20entrepreneur%20behind%20a%20millet-based%20brand%2C%20offers%20a%20diverse%20range%20of%20millet%20products%20through%20his%20startup.%20From%20Jowar%20Flakes%20to%20Millet%20Muesli%20and%20Millet%20Idli%20Rawa%20pre-mix%2C%20the%20brand%20aims%20to%20seamlessly%20integrate%20this%20superfood%20into%20your%20daily%20diet.%20With%20thousands%20of%20products%20sold%2C%20the%20brand%20has%20achieved%20an%20impressive%20annual%20revenue%20of%20Rs%202.5%20crores.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98For%20a%20healthy%20and%20long%20life%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20his%20engineering%20from%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Sai%20decided%20to%20take%20a%20corporate%20job%20in%20the%20education%20sector.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20I%20was%20working%20a%20job%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20get%20into%20ventureship.%20I%20had%20always%20dreamt%20of%20being%20an%20entrepreneur.%20I%20was%20only%20waiting%20for%20the%20right%20idea%20to%20come%20along%20for%20me%20to%20take%20the%20leap%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESai%20recalls%20that%20while%20he%20was%20in%20college%2C%20he%20wanted%20to%20set%20up%20his%20own%20business%20and%20had%20a%20couple%20of%20ideas%20too.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20there%20were%20a%20lot%20of%20ideas%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20that%20stood%20out%20and%20was%20benefitting%20the%20society%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%