0Shahani%20(currently%20a%20director%20at%20Praan)%2C%20helped%20obtain%20an%20unsecured%20loan%20of%20%2415%2C000%20to%20fund%20the%20research%20and%20development.%20Taken%20in%20Angad%E2%80%99s%20name%2C%20this%20sum%20was%20eventually%20doubled%20and%20returned%20in%202021.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20that%20summer%2C%20Angad%2C%20his%20TA%20and%20two%20interns%20put%20together%20the%20prototype%20of%20what%20would%20become%20the%20MKOne%20Outdoor%20Air%20Purifier.%20The%20plan%20moving%20forward%20was%20that%20Angad%20would%20graduate%20in%202020%2C%20run%20this%20company%20full-time%20after%20graduating%2C%20and%20raise%20capital.%20Despite%20his%20best%20efforts%2C%20securing%20funding%20was%20a%20major%20challenge.%20By%20January%202020%2C%20investors%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20caught%20on%20to%20the%20potential%20of%20deep%20tech%20and%20the%20offers%20on%20the%20table%20were%20not%20satisfactory.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20challenges%2C%20he%20managed%20%E2%80%9Cto%20pool%20together%20some%20soft%20commitments%20worth%20%241.35M%20from%20an%20Indian%20VC%20fund%20and%20a%20few%20strategic%20angels%20on%20very%20bad%20investment%20terms%E2%80%9D.%20As%20these%20deals%20were%20being%20finalised%2C%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20struck%20and%20everything%20fell%20apart.%20Yet%20to%20graduate%20from%20college%2C%20he%20had%20to%20pack%20everything%20up%20and%20come%20back%20to%20India%20while%20completing%20online%20classes%20to%20get%20his%20degree.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20was%20a%20silver%20lining.%20Since%20people%20were%20losing%20their%20jobs%20and%20internships%2C%20there%20were%20many%20looking%20to%20work%20on%20something%20that%20would%20advance%20their%20careers.%20Similar%20to%20what%20he%20did%20earlier%2C%20Angad%20offered%20recognition%20on%20Praan%20patents%20to%20anyone%20who%20helped%20develop%20the%20technology%20further%20either%20remotely%20or%20even%20as%20a%20volunteer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20total%2C%20Praan%20managed%20to%20onboard%20about%2060%20volunteers%20from%20multiple%20time%20zones%20who%20chose%20to%20dedicate%20about%20four%20months%20of%20their%20time%20to%20work%20on%20their%20technology.%C2%A0%20While%20the%20hardware%20was%20built%20and%20developed%20out%20of%20Angad%20and%20his%20intern%E2%80%99s%20bedrooms%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337225%2Fvolunteer-beach-cleanup-akshat-shah-shubh-mehta-mumbai-new-year-resolution%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMumbai%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20other%20volunteers%20from%20around%20the%20world%20contributed%20with%20their%20ideas%20and%20engineering%20drawings%20for%20their%20prototypes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Praan%20website%2C%20there%20were%20also%20%E2%80%9Cdesign%20teams%20working%20on%20ideas%20for%20the%20MK%20One%20product%2C%20the%20indoor%20air%20purification%2C%20bioengineering%2C%20carbon%20capture%2C%20and%20software%20engineering%20products%E2%80%94all%20without%20any%20capital%20in%20the%20bank%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReal%20funding%20and%20assistance%20finally%20came%20in%20the%20form%20of%20Emergent%20Ventures%2C%20a%20fellowship%20and%20grant%20programme%20run%20by%20famous%20economist%20Dr.%20Tyler%20Cowen.%20It%20gave%20this%20fledgling%20startup%20the%20largest%20grant%20during%20the%20lockdown%20period%20which%20helped%20them%20access%20capital%20to%20build%20prototypes%20and%20test%20rigs%20as%20well.%20In%20the%20next%20few%20months%2C%20they%20developed%20a%20working%20prototype%20of%20the%20MKOne%20Outdoor%20Air%20purifier%20in%20India.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20was%20very%20little%20customer%20or%20investor%20interest%20and%20a%20negligible%20amount%20of%20vendors%20were%20willing%20to%20manufacture%20the%20MKOne%20prototype.%20Angad%20spent%20about%20five%20months%20waiting%20for%20vendors%20to%20manufacture%20the%20first%20usable%20MKOne%20pr