0mother.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Gaurav%20Sabharwal%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20did%20the%20first%20thing%20that%20most%20people%20would%20do%20%E2%80%94%20go%20on%20the%20internet%20and%20read%20up%20about%20aeroponics.%20I%20found%20a%20bunch%20of%20people%20growing%20saffron%20using%20the%20technique%2C%20and%20I%20decided%20to%20contact%20them%2C%20reaching%20out%20for%20their%20help%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20the%20research%20that%20he%20found%20out%20the%20amount%20of%20money%20he%20would%20need%20to%20set%20up%20his%20farm%20lab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20did%20not%20have%20that%20kind%20of%20investment%2C%20so%20I%20sought%20help%20from%20the%20government.%20I%20got%20a%20loan%20of%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20and%20even%20got%20a%20rebate%20under%20PM%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20startup%20scheme%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20right%20investment%20in%20hand%2C%20Gaurav%20was%20ready%20to%20try%20his%20hand%20at%20growing%20saffron%20in%20Solan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20greatest%20factor%20to%20consider%20was%20that%20the%20temperature%20needed%20to%20grow%20saffron%20was%20only%20in%20Kashmir%20in%20India.%20So%20I%20had%20to%20mimic%20that%20here%20in%20Solan.%20I%20used%20the%20lab%20whose%20temperature%20can%20be%20controlled%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20mimicking%20the%20environment%20and%20planting%20the%20seeds%2C%20it%20was%20important%20for%20me%20to%20keep%20a%20close%20eye%20on%20the%20buds.%20I%20was%20not%20aware%20that%20they%20can%20catch%20fungus%20and%20was%20taken%20aback%20when%20my%20first%20crop%20did%20catch%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20able%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20it%20by%20drying%20the%20affected%20plants%20and%20separating%20them%20from%20the%20healthy%20ones%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20nearly%208%20months%20of%20hard%20labour%20and%20p